replies.body:
I honestly liked the way Riot responded to the player feedback, they responded in quite a positive manner, using the negative mantra that is the majority of League of Legends's members. It just shows that Riot **does** respond to what we want, and **does** go the extra mile to help make the game better!
Well done Riot!! Thanks!
I will defs be buying that SKT T1 Syndra skin, Faker himself said it would give us Pentakill power!! {{sticker:slayer-jinx-wink}}
